STRUCT ID(Pt) LBRACE
INT ID(x) COMMA ID(y) SEMICOLON
RBRACE SEMICOLON

STRUCT ID(Pt) ID(points) LBRACKET CT_INT(20) DIV CT_INT(4) PLUS CT_INT(5) RBRACKET SEMICOLON

INT ID(count) LPAREN RPAREN
LBRACE
INT ID(i) COMMA ID(n) SEMICOLON
FOR LPAREN ID(i) ASSIGN ID(n) ASSIGN CT_INT(0) SEMICOLON ID(i) LT CT_INT(10) SEMICOLON ID(i) ASSIGN ID(i) PLUS CT_INT(1) RPAREN LBRACE
IF LPAREN ID(points) LBRACKET ID(i) RBRACKET DOT ID(x) GE CT_INT(0) AND ID(points) LBRACKET ID(i) RBRACKET DOT ID(y) GE CT_INT(0) RPAREN ID(n) ASSIGN ID(n) PLUS CT_INT(1) SEMICOLON
RBRACE
RETURN ID(n) SEMICOLON
RBRACE

VOID ID(main) LPAREN RPAREN
LBRACE
ID(put_i) LPAREN ID(count) LPAREN RPAREN RPAREN SEMICOLON
RBRACE
